casebody.data:
Richard J. KURZBAN, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The BANK OF NEW YORK MELLON, etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1116 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 14, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and FERNANDEZ and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 24, 2018, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
